---
title: 語料清理管線 (L22403)
---
flowchart LR
    RAW["🌐 原始語料\nCommon Crawl\n~100TB HTML"]
    EXT["📄 文字萃取\nHTML → Plain Text\n移除標記/CSS/JS"]
    LANG["🌏 語言識別\nfastText LangDetect\n過濾非目標語言"]
    QUAL["⭐ 品質過濾\nPerplexity Filter\n規則過濾 (短句/亂碼)"]
    DEDUP["🔍 去重\nExact-match Hash\nMinHash LSH Near-dedup\n減少 20–30%"]
    SAFE["🛡️ 安全過濾\nPII 偵測\n有害內容過濾"]
    TOK["✂️ 分詞\nBPE / SentencePiece\n→ Token IDs"]
    OUT["✅ 訓練語料\n~15TB tokens\n(C4 from CC)"]

    RAW --> EXT --> LANG --> QUAL --> DEDUP --> SAFE --> TOK --> OUT

